mnar emphasis) or Songaksan + Hyeopjae (volcano + beach emphasis).", "score_rationale": {"high_scores": {"ocean_falling_waterfall_fit=1.0": "Jeongbang Falls is the only waterfall in Asia falling directly into the ocean", "value_for_money_fit=0.95": "Almost all stops are free; only Jeongbang Falls charges ~₩2,000 — densest free-admission Jeju loop", "coastal_scenery_fit=1.0": "Jeongbang Falls + Oedolgae sea stack + Olle 7 coastal walk = strong Seogwipo coast focus", "tea_enthusiast_fit=1.0": "Osulloc + Seogwang Dawon = Korea''s tea-culture flagship destination", "temple_fit=1.0": "Yakcheonsa — one of the largest Buddhist temple complexes in East Asia", "yeongjusipgyeong_fit=0.85": "Jeongbang Falls + Hallasan are both among Jeju''s 10 Scenic Wonders"}, "low_scores": {"private_tour_fit=0.05": "Format is small-group fixed itinerary only", "east_jeju_fit=0.05": "Loop deliberately south + Seogwipo anchored", "rain_fit=0.4": "Only Osulloc interior and Yakcheonsa hall are reliable rain refuges; most stops are outdoor coast/trail", "botanical_garden_fit=0.0": "No botanical garden on this route (sister tour covers Camellia Hill)"}}, "differentiation_vs_west_south_authentic_sister": "Shares the Osulloc + Hallasan anchors, but leads with the **Seogwipo coastal trio** — Jeongbang Falls (Asia''s only ocean-plunging waterfall), Oedolgae sea stack + Olle Trail 7, and Yakcheonsa (East Asia''s largest temple) — instead of the sister tour''s Jusangjeolli columnar cliff + Cheonjeyeon + Camellia Hill botanical emphasis. This tour = coast + temple + tea + Hallasan UNESCO, almost entirely free admission; sister = waterfalls + columnar geology + year-round flower garden. Pair complementarily for guests with 2 days on Jeju.", "seasonal_window": {"best_months": ["April", "May", "October", "November", "March (cherry start)"], "good_months": ["June", "September", "December", "February"], "caveat_months": ["July (monsoon)", "August (heat + crowds)", "January (Hallasan/1100 Road ice)"], "peak_crowd_months": ["April (cherry)", "October (foliage)"]}, "kb_anchor_version": "1.29"}'::jsonb,
